   body 
      header.header 
         h1.header__title
            | Learn to code by 
            br
            | watching others
         p.header__description See how experienced developers solve problems in real-time. Watching scripted tutorials is great, but understanding how developers think is invaluable. 
      main.main 
         h2.main__title
            span.main__plans Try it free 7 days 
            | then $20/mo. thereafter
         form.form#form(action="#") 
            input.form__input(type="text", name="firstname", placeholder="First Name", aria-label="Fist Name")
            input.form__input(type="text", name="lastname", placeholder="Last Name", aria-label="Last Name")
            input.form__input(type="email", name="email", placeholder="Email Address", aria-label="Email")
            input.form__input(type="password", name="password", placeholder="Password", aria-label="Password")
            button.form__submit(type="submit") Claim your free trial
            p.form__condition
               | By clicking the button, you are agreeing to our 
               span.form__terms Terms and Services
      script(src="js/scripts-min.js") 
            
